
Java programming to compute tf-idf over a corpus
------------------------------------------------

* To stage suitable data, use shakespeare-stream.tar.gz:

	cp ../../data/shakespeare-stream.tar.gz .
	tar zxvf shakespeare-stream.tar.gz
	hadoop fs -put shakespeare-stream shakespeare-stream

  or use shakespeare-stream-fragment.tar, for tiny input:

	tar xvf shakespeare-stream-fragment.tar
	mv shakespeare-stream-fragment shakespeare-stream
	hadoop fs -put shakespeare-stream shakespeare-stream

  Data can be used in HDFS or local filesystem (add "-fs file:///" to runs)

* To compile and jar:

	build

* To execute: 

	run
  or
	runjtlocal (for local job tracker)

